flowchart LR
  Wireframe[Wireframe] --> TestWireframe[Test wireframe]
  TestWireframe --> RefineStructure[Refine structure]
  RefineStructure --> VisualDesign[Visual design]
  VisualDesign --> TestVisual[Test visual design]
  TestVisual --> Prototype[Coded or clickable prototype]
  Prototype --> QA[QA and release checks]
  TestWireframe -- usability issue --> Wireframe
  TestVisual -- hierarchy or trust issue --> VisualDesign
  QA -- implementation drift --> Prototype
